        class="text-base tablet:text-sm tablet:w-[30rem] mobile:w-full text-light-200 mt-8 tablet:mt-4 h-[8.75rem] tablet:h-[6.875rem] mobile:h-[8.125rem]"
      >
        Participate in Sahara Data, a trustless, permissionless, and
        privacy-preserving platform for high-value datasets and data services to
        train AI.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div
    id="bookDemo2"
    class="mx-auto w-[27rem] tablet:w-40 mobile:w-full mobile:text-xs border whitespace-nowrap text-sm  h-11 py-2.5 px-4 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl common-button"
