        > offers an intelligent AI-centered, human-in-the-loop, and privacy-preserving
        approach to generate <span class="text-light-100">High Value</span> datasets
        for your AI.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="font-[Manrope] mb-[7.5rem] tablet:mb-[3.75rem]">
    <div
      class="text-light-200 text-h5 mobile:text-s3 mobile:text-center mb-[3.75rem] mobile:mb-8"
